00:43:20.140 --> 00:43:25.000
to zero as nu goes to zero; this
e to the minus very negative

00:43:25.000 --> 00:43:25.610
stuff is zero.

00:43:25.610 --> 00:43:33.000
But we have a nu here, so in the
