00:52:58.210 --> 00:53:02.880
OK, so that's a little
history, with no details,

00:53:02.880 --> 00:53:07.770
of an incredibly special
class of nonlinear PDEs.

00:53:07.770 --> 00:53:12.320
Well of course, the
